  "meta": {
    "name": "Base RWA ST0x - wire collateral-only replacement vaults",
    "description": "Wires the replacement collateral-only wtSPYM, wtMSTR, and wtCOIN EVaults into the existing AlphaGrowth Base RWA market. Updates the shared EulerRouter to use Euler AggregatorV3 adapters, removes deprecated ST0x vaults from router resolution, resolves the replacement vaults, and lets the existing eUSDC vault accept the replacement vaults as collateral. Execute after old ST0x vault LTVs/caps are decommissioned. This payload does not activate hooks, set IRMs, set reverse LTVs, change caps, or transfer governance."
  },
